                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h5><span class="join-type join-left">LEFT JOIN</span></h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">返回左表的所有记录，以及右表中匹配的记录。如果右表没有匹配的记录，则右表字段为NULL。</p>
                        <div class="code-block">
join="left admin.store_id = store.store_id"
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h5><span class="join-type join-right">RIGHT JOIN</span></h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">返回右表的所有记录，以及左表中匹配的记录。如果左表没有匹配的记录，则左表字段为NULL。</p>
                        <div class="code-block">
join="right store.store_id = admin.store_id"
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h5><span class="join-type join-inner">INNER JOIN</span></h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">只返回两个表中都有匹配记录的记录。这是最常用的JOIN类型。</p>
                        <div class="code-block">
join="inner admin.username = config.scope"
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h5><span class="join-type join-outer">OUTER JOIN</span></h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">返回两个表中的所有记录，无论是否匹配。不匹配的字段为NULL。</p>
                        <div class="code-block">
join="outer admin.id = config.id"
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

